19
00:01:46,740 --> 00:01:47,330
No hurry.

20
00:01:47,910 --> 00:01:49,070
You'll know later.

21
00:02:06,510 --> 00:02:07,480
Are you sure

22
00:02:07,710 --> 00:02:09,150
she has transferred the dock

23
00:02:09,150 --> 00:02:10,039
to you?

24
00:02:10,669 --> 00:02:11,520
Don't worry.

25
00:02:12,070 --> 00:02:14,070
We've already signed the contract.

26
00:02:14,160 --> 00:02:14,840
By then,

27
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:17,230
let's change the dock to gold.

28
00:02:17,910 --> 00:02:18,910
Baby,

29
00:02:19,230 --> 00:02:22,070
we can go away together.

30
00:02:22,070 --> 00:02:22,600
Good.

31
00:02:23,190 --> 00:02:25,510
Thank you for your hard work these days.

32
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:28,190
You've sacrificed yourself to serve that woman.

33
00:02:28,190 --> 00:02:30,030
I wonder what's so good about her.

34
00:02:30,030 --> 00:02:32,630
Why did Master Shen marry her as his concubine?

35
00:02:33,470 --> 00:02:34,150
Alright.

36
00:02:34,470 --> 00:02:35,870
Let's not talk about her.

37
00:02:36,150 --> 00:02:37,070
Now,

38
00:02:37,630 --> 00:02:39,470
